Business-driven data storytelling

 Conclusion:

This analysis demonstrates how combining KPI tracking, funnel analysis, and customer segmentation can provide actionable insights into churn behavior. By focusing on early warning signals and high-risk segments, the business can proactively reduce churn and improve long-term performance.